{"Id":560375,"Title":"近田辞","Dynasty":"明","Author":"孙承恩","Context":"惟道在人，不远伊迩。求道于远，道则非是。近义云何，为切为亲。随处随在，目击道存。则匪汗漫，则匪浮誇。愈近愈真，愈远愈差。是故善学，鞭辟近里。本之于身，以达于事。即类取譬，充义达为。是谓一贯，粗精显微。许子有田，近也匪逖。惟志之占，惟道之的。许子恂恂，本实是敦。崇虚饰无，则匪其人。我言许子，厥犹有义。匪近惟田，心性之喻。故曰圣王，人情为田。田而弗治，稊稗生焉。毕力尽瘁，惟农之良。礼耕义植，人情之防。许子勉旃，夙夜祗惕。庶几寡愆，以厚其德。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"c7d130cc9cef382fdbead37ec66dc3af","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6670420,"Sentence":"惟道在人，不远伊迩。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wéi dāo zài rén ，bú yuǎn yī ěr ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670421,"Sentence":"求道于远，道则非是。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qǐu dāo yú yuǎn ，dāo zé fēi shì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670422,"Sentence":"近义云何，为切为亲。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jìn yǐ yún hé ，wéi qiē wéi qīn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670423,"Sentence":"随处随在，目击道存。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"suǐ chǔ suǐ zài ，mù jī dāo cún ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670424,"Sentence":"则匪汗漫，则匪浮誇。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zé fěi hán màn ，zé fěi fú kuā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670425,"Sentence":"愈近愈真，愈远愈差。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yù jìn yù zhēn ，yù yuǎn yù chā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670426,"Sentence":"是故善学，鞭辟近里。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shì gù shàn xué ，biān bì jìn li ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670427,"Sentence":"本之于身，以达于事。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"běn zhī yú shēn ，yi dá yú shì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6670428,"Sentence":"即类取譬，充义达为。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jǐ lèi qǔ pì ，chōng yǐ dá wéi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8